  * Sisu has moved to Eclipse! *
  ==============================
  
  This repository contains wrappers that allow legacy Sonatype/Sisu applications to work with Eclipse/Sisu.
  
  Homepage
  ========
  <http://eclipse.org/sisu>
  
  Wiki
  ====
  <http://wiki.eclipse.org/Sisu>
  
  Issue Tracker
