not missing setup.\",\"deterministic_setup\":[],\"agent_guidance\":\"No environment or system-property setup is required. Generated tests should target the 2.4.2 transitive Eclipse Sisu API; in particular, avoid carrying over the old three-argument QualifiedTypeBinder.hear call and use the available two-argument form instead.\",\"risks\":[\"The artifact has optional JUnit 4, TestNG, SLF4J, and OSGi dependencies, but they are only needed if tests deliberately exercise those optional/deprecated integration surfaces; core bean scanning, binding, URLClassSpace, and SisuGuice coverage is reachable without them.\",\"Existing 2.4.0 tests may need source updates for API signature changes when run against 2.4.2.\"]}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_091ad1d25e3d5b4d016a3ff0c395b88194b658b81ddeb7ba72\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 529, "output": 1242, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29419, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782575282179, "responseId": "resp_091ad1d25e3d5b4d016a3ff0b2aef08194862e676a7fab1e25"}}
